Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.87,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}このままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.71,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}そう思っていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.08,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:55.97,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}胸の中閉じ込めたキャンバスに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.80,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:05.81,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}失った未来さえ描いてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.36,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}空のように
