Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:36.20,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}在漆黑一片的地方  独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.87,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}自己的存在无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.87,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}静静地呆着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.71,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}这样的想法曾是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.08,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:55.97,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}在我埋藏于心中的油画布上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.80,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:05.81,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}你为我描绘出已经失去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:20.16,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}怀着如同湛蓝天空般清澈的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:27.66,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}想与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还听说  榊是小老婆生的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说她本来是跟父亲分开生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后来作为继承人的弟弟去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就被唤回了本家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把这种事说出来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田同学你最近跟榊同学不是相处得挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为传出去才能收到更多有趣的信息嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  你可真毒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你的脸色看起来不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是感到有什么不适的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来陪你去校医室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  没有一个安身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我现在已经找到了没有那种地方也能活下去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与造成伤人事件时相比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子同学的精神已经非常安定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们的调查员虽然在刚接触时有所冲突…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春寺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:08.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40.8}东滨电铁：源自日本实存的铁路公司「京急电铁」（京滨急行电铁）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的是由美子尽快做好成为我东滨电铁集团成员的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的调查员  名字是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫风见雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总裁  他的本分还是学生  只是兼任…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吩咐他劝诫由美子回心转意乖乖返回本家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的组织不做心理辅导和洗脑之类的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  让我的手下去袭击由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让她尝尝恐惧的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她就会屈服于恐惧乖乖听我的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是您决定用这种计划的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给您一个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  幸  你把那线路占了我就真要破产啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我在此手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏的紧张感就会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为满大小姐着想而做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这还为我着想  你把那占了我都不用玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你真是虐人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来满满的生路就断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我也不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥最近总是跟着由美子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不玩了不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜  今天就直接去买东西吧  来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过厕纸会扯痛我手指
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以天姐你要自己拿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  最近老在我周围转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当我是路边的石头好了  由美由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想一脚踢飞你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  保护榊由美子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她身为东滨电铁集团总裁的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被各种各样的人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要让我一个人保护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我要你保护她并且吃点亏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这程度哪里称得上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜欢画才画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是无话可说权当消遣罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要画着画就不需要跟人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢一个人呆着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不擅长与人交往而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很无聊的女人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画的评价我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过把自己评价成这样的女人确实感觉不到魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不问为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要我问我就问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不想说我就不问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我受不了打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕  好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我从不觉得自己强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样一个人也能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲跟我母亲结婚是想要她生一个接班的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但生下来的却是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身子弱的母亲已经无法再生第二胎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和接受榊家援助的母亲娘家都责怪她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使她身心都患病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终被在意脸面的外公外婆送进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲变成了孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被风言风语和好奇的视线包围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连朋友都交不到一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家时外公外婆都当我是碍事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  我还是每天都去探望母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我期盼着总有一天她能再次对我微笑  直至那一天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我明天再来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你是男孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是  自愿成为这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要  不要再这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是男孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为  就因为这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲之后跟情人生了个男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而这件事刺激了母亲导致她自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后她都在为没能生男孩而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我那弟弟也因病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲把我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当做什么都没发生过一样想把我培养为继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个人来说  我和母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的一切都只不过是扩张东滨集团的道具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于母亲的自杀和弟弟的死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的周围充满了好奇的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是在家还是在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有一个能让我放心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我渐渐承受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用美工刀砍伤了嘲笑我的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲为掩人耳目而建了个学校把我藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是美滨学园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是从笼中鸟变成了墙中鸟罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的价值就只有成为那个家的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点也不是我自己获取的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我为父亲和母亲所生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本人根本毫无价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像废话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思让你陪我这种毫无价值的人这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实都是些废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你为什么想一个人呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那个男人进行了抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟说好的可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻让那个叫风见什么东西的男人退学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子好不容易才安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又闹出事该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是会做那种事的学生…虽然我也不敢保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意我就让由美子去美国留学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们学校也将关闭  赶紧办通手续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留学？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你的父亲说如果你不愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就把风见同学赶出学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃点  养得圆滚滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学  出来把话说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  我有事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  为什么由美子不从房里出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满大小姐  刚才校长已经说明过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见同学偏偏这种时候跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他说这与我无关就回房去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙好无情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起想办法吧  榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我老实出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没空理会不听命令的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是这里的管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是这的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话快把由美子交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学现在很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能请您再给她一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那种闲情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后的行程还都排满着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,充大忙人嚣张个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那丫头是在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是满  松岛满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间你就赶紧滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子现在没空理你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你听懂了就赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好满满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太好了满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等会我给您一块方糖当奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不该让由美子跟这些小丫头混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也住得比榊家舒服得多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会亲自重新教育你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你培养成东滨电铁集团的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西  你是从哪弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,买的  网上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手  枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  真枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是华尔瑟PPK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,德国华尔瑟公司开发的警用手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目测口径为32
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹量为7+1发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:15:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵  我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  就让我们开始交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经让学生们到教学楼避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事将由我们自己秘密处理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  就是为了这种时候我才给你们资金的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别干傻事给我出来吧由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是连你也跟美佐子一样离我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就真变成孤零零一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说笑话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都忘了你对我和妈妈做了什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈被你抛弃后一直孤零零一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我被妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们  全都是孤零零一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊家这种地方没落掉最好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止都为继承人的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来没有为我着想过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你被榊家的诅咒缠身了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想变成你那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为就你自己受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲托给我的大东滨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岂能因你一个小丫头的任性而衰落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  回榊家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会任由你摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以自己的意志开口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会当你的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  虽然你没理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也没尝试过去理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种孽缘就由我们来斩断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始就没存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们带他们去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你留下学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是在她房间找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着就算她不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望我能继续经营美滨学园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那孩子第一次也是最后一次对我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子在最后留给我的那个表情  那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,印刻在我的心里消散不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子拼上了性命教了我某些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在以后的人生里慢慢思考她教给我的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有你这样的女儿是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这次分开之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于有点理解爸爸的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我至今仍厌恶自己降生在榊家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过能生为爸爸和妈妈的孩子这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经能感到有些幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不打算干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这对我们来说是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs39.667\fr270\pos(1254.017,234)}我们被监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs39.667\fr270\pos(998.668,226)}关于你父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs39.667\fr270\pos(649.983,219.6)}我会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs39.667\fr270\pos(406.238,214.8)}你自己决定自己该走的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在狙击成功前我也心慌慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟榊小姐的第一发可是实弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好没有新手运气加成让她打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲托给我的大东滨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岂能因你一个小丫头的任性而衰落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有准备尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真让我大伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪雄二你违抗命令才把事闹得这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这又不是通过正式的手续接到的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以现场判断为准
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耍嘴皮倒是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有周围的窃听器都回收完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是这个  户籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在风波平静之前你可得安分点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你将从这里开始新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来风见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  你怎么可能只是个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也基本猜得出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笔触  跟之前不一样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  幸福的信
